1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,930
Let's each do what we're good at.

2
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

3
00:00:03,120 --> 00:00:04,350
Do I fascinate you?

4
00:00:04,830 --> 00:00:07,080
Am I an animal at the zoo?

5
00:00:07,470 --> 00:00:08,620
Get out.

6
00:00:09,010 --> 00:00:11,520
Could you please get lost?

7
00:00:13,720 --> 00:00:15,610
I just don't get you.

8
00:00:15,700 --> 00:00:17,550
You'd never be able to.

9
00:00:17,640 --> 00:00:19,750
Then enlighten me.
I want to understand you.

10
00:00:19,840 --> 00:00:21,990
Why should I even bother?

11
00:00:22,480 --> 00:00:24,720
Why should I
when I'm neck-deep in my own worries?

12
00:00:34,580 --> 00:00:37,700
It's past midnight
and the bed isn't refundable.

13
00:00:37,920 --> 00:00:40,170
Insisting that you take off at this hour

14
00:00:40,250 --> 00:00:41,660
won't change a thing.

15
00:00:42,760 --> 00:00:44,080
Get at least a good night's sleep.

16
00:00:45,400 --> 00:00:47,380
I see money is what you understand.

17
00:00:48,310 --> 00:00:51,250
My words carry no weight, but money does.

18
00:00:53,810 --> 00:00:55,650
I'll get lost then.

19
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:02,560
It's time for your shot.

20
00:01:02,650 --> 00:01:06,040
Could you make sure
the pain is unbearable?

21
00:01:17,830 --> 00:01:20,730
Don't skip your meals
and ventilate the room often.

22
