[Storytelling Marketing]

28
00:02:15,950 --> 00:02:17,630
[The girl I like...]

29
00:02:21,230 --> 00:02:23,480
No way. I memorized what he said.

30
00:02:24,010 --> 00:02:25,500
Instead of memorizing lecture notes...

31
00:02:26,690 --> 00:02:28,010
Darn it.

32
00:02:28,190 --> 00:02:30,780
[Don't tell me
he confessed his love to you.]

33
00:02:31,130 --> 00:02:32,410
Please don't say that's true.

34
00:02:34,430 --> 00:02:37,430
Of course not.
Don't you worry and go to bed.

35
00:02:37,780 --> 00:02:39,050
No one-sided love is allowed.

36
00:02:39,140 --> 00:02:41,780
You're one to let it go on
for at least 14 years.

37
00:02:42,050 --> 00:02:43,500
Let me do that math.

38
00:02:43,850 --> 00:02:46,579
She'll only have experienced
unrequited love twice at 36.

39
00:02:48,510 --> 00:02:50,540
-Really?
-Your hair looks great.

40
00:02:50,630 --> 00:02:52,390
Maybe it's because it's black.

41
00:02:54,230 --> 00:02:57,140
My gosh. You're so handsome!

42
00:02:59,730 --> 00:03:02,070
No way. Not a chance!

43
00:03:02,150 --> 00:03:04,050
Darn, I'm done sleeping.

44
00:03:04,710 --> 00:03:05,760
So-bin!

45
00:03:16,060 --> 00:03:18,170
What's the excuse for drinking
this time around?

46
00:03:24,860 --> 00:03:27,760
He won't take my calls.
That's why I can't sleep.

47
00:03:28,420 --> 00:03:31,060
-Who?
-This darn idiot.

48
00:03:31,370 --> 00:03:32,560
-A guy?
-A guy?

49
00:03:32,650 --> 00:03:33,829
What?

50
00:03:34,579 --> 00:03:38,720
He's like a thorn embedded in my chest.

51
00:03:40,350 --> 00:03:42,410
-A thorn!
-A thorn!

52
00:03:42,500 --> 00:03:44,610
What's gotten into you two tonight?

53
00:03:44,700 --> 00:03:45,980
Are you already drunk?

54
00:03:46,070 --> 00:03:47,780
You're not one to talk about guys.

55
00:03:47,870 --> 00:03:49,450
Mostly exercising and drinking.

56
00:03:49,850 --> 00:03:50,950
Who is this guy?

57
00:03:52,230 --> 00:03:55,750
He's a thorn that's stuck in deep,

58
00:03:56,540 --> 00:03:58,470
so it hurts.

59
00:03:58,560 --> 00:04:01,110
Why love someone
who'd only give you heartache?

60
00:04:01,470 --> 00:04:02,920
You should've kept it casual.

61
00:04:03,530 --> 00:04:06,350
Why love someone
who you need to make excuses to see?

62
00:04:06,920 --> 00:04:09,560
Who? You?

63
00:04:09,650 --> 00:04:10,750
Me?

64
00:04:12,950 --> 00:04:15,060
Wait. Is this room cursed?

65
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:17,880
Why is everyone
suffering from unrequited love?

66
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:20,690
No, not me.

67
00:04:21,269 --> 00:04:23,200
I'm done with one-sided love.

68
00:04:23,730 --> 00:04:25,580
I'd rather die a relationship virgin

69
00:04:25,670 --> 00:04:27,290
than love someone
who doesn't love me back.

70
00:04:27,380 --> 00:04:29,010
As if you can control that.

71
00:04:29,100 --> 00:04:31,250
This isn't something
you can write a declaration for.

72
00:04:32,050 --> 00:04:33,980
Whatever. Let's just drink.

73
00:04:34,330 --> 00:04:35,480
But I'll gain weight.

74
00:04:35,570 --> 00:04:37,630
The calories will be split three ways.

75
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:40,140
Rather than gaining the whole 3kg,
we'll gain 1kg each.

76
00:04:40,230 --> 00:04:41,240
Sounds good.

77
00:04:41,330 --> 00:04:43,530
It'll be 3kg each and a total of 9kg.

78
00:04:43,620 --> 00:04:44,670
Unbelievable.

79
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:50,090
Let's be loyal friends
and gain weight together.

80
00:04:59,110 --> 00:05:00,250
Cheers.

81
00:05:03,990 --> 00:05:05,180
That's a big bite.

82
00:05:05,490 --> 00:05:06,720
It's good.

