90
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:33,480
I can work, sir.

91
00:06:33,570 --> 00:06:35,820
A youngster who used to work with us

92
00:06:35,900 --> 00:06:37,490
died last month.

93
00:06:38,280 --> 00:06:40,080
He was studying for the state exam.

94
00:06:40,300 --> 00:06:41,800
I'm fine, sir.

95
00:06:42,550 --> 00:06:43,600
That night--

96
00:06:43,690 --> 00:06:46,600
You work nights after
taking classes during the day, right?

97
00:06:47,870 --> 00:06:49,980
-Yes.
-Then study hard

98
00:06:50,070 --> 00:06:51,520
and find a less demanding job.

99
00:06:53,060 --> 00:06:54,650
It's all for your sake.

100
