Do you have any night shifts available?

102
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:17,480
[Job search: Night shifts]

103
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:20,560
Hello? I'm calling about

104
00:07:20,650 --> 00:07:22,810
the school cafeteria job.

105
00:07:23,820 --> 00:07:26,060
Right, I see.

106
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:42,780
Hey, Mom.

107
00:07:43,710 --> 00:07:45,860
It's the weekend. Are you well?

108
00:07:48,370 --> 00:07:50,530
I sent some money to Uncle.

109
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,840
Don't worry about
Koo-hyun's rent at the gosiwon.

110
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:58,270
It's all right.

111
00:08:02,010 --> 00:08:03,070
Mom.

112
00:08:05,490 --> 00:08:07,290
What if I dropped out of school?

113
00:08:09,050 --> 00:08:10,770
No, it's not like that.

114
00:08:14,420 --> 00:08:16,400
All right, sure.

115
